1. *Broju* dece u ovoj školi je porastao u poslednjih pet godina. (The *number* of children in this school has increased in the last five years.)
2. Molim vas da mi kažete *broj* vašeg telefona. (Please tell me your *phone number*.)
3. Želim da kupim *broj* tri cipele u crnoj boji. (I want to buy *size* three shoes in black.)
4. *Brojila* su se pokvarila i ne rade više. (The *counters* broke down and don't work anymore.)
5. Želimo da *brojimo* na srpskom do deset. (We want to *count* in Serbian up to ten.)
6. Ovo je *broj* jedan razlog zašto treba da putujete u Srbiju. (This is *number* one reason why you should travel to Serbia.)
7. Imamo *brojne* dokaze koji potvrđuju naše tvrdnje. (We have *numerous* evidence to support our claims.)
8. Ova knjiga se prodala u *velikom broju* primeraka. (This book has been sold in a *large number* of copies.)
9. Molim vas da *brojite* do deset pre nego što napravite sledeći potez. (Please *count* to ten before you make your next move.)
10. U ovom restoranu postoji *broj* vegetarijanskih jela. (This restaurant has a *number* of vegetarian dishes.)